ore":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T09:13:33.000Z","msg":"成日話推畀對家就係割<br />\n乜手足做黎係為左攞彩？"},{"pid":"4fb649845526d5e6dc20cbca448a5f438ffc2b7d","tid":1813292,"uid":62609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T10:40:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b4992fd0f47c5c80b93d46823f56764a5da5609","tid":1813292,"uid":49178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T10:52:45.000Z","msg":"其實唔洗理咩人做<br />\n你覺得間鋪頭抵死<br />\n大叫一句掟得好就得啦"},{"pid":"88178d4872b7331031898c26d4193eacd5235c05","tid":1813292,"uid":297672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T11:27:24.000Z","msg":"咩推！？個個大大隻包到成個賊咁，爆完舖又冇畀人拉，仲唔係臥底？有哂前科啦。<br />\n<br />\n傻鳩先會爭住認，好撚型好威風啊？？我哋良好市民嚟㗎。"},{"pid":"e49874e81bec02fbe6c3b35b65ff86da938f04a7","tid":1813292,"uid":62609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T12:23:55.000Z","msg":"推"}]}